      <b data-is-speakable>Coronavirus Spurs Demand For Face Masks — But They're Surprisingly Hard To make : Goats and Soda</b>   <b data-is-speakable>China makes millions of masks. But ramping up production is tricky. "Making masks is not as easy as you imagine," a pharmaceutical executive in China says.</b>
