    </h3>
</div>
<div class="storytitle">
      <h1>COVID-19 Has Caused A Shortage Of Face Masks. But They're Surprisingly Hard To Make</h1>
   <input type="hidden" id="title814929294" value="COVID-19 Has Caused A Shortage Of Face Masks. But They're Surprisingly Hard To Make" />
   <input type="hidden" id="shortTitle814929294" value="COVID-19 Has Caused A Shortage Of Face Masks. But They're Surprisingly Hard To Make" />
